verbose_text: The expression of the BAD mediated apoptotic pathway was associated with the development and/or progression of ovarian (n = 106, p < 0.001), breast (n = 185, p < 0.0008; n = 61, p = 0.04), colon (n = 22, p < 0.001) and endometrial (n = 33, p < 0.001) cancers, as well as with ovarian endometriosis (n = 20, p < 0.001).
